        public ExperimentCounts getExperimentRollup(Experiment.ID experimentID,
                                            Parameters parameters)
        Returns a number of summary counts for the specified experiment, using rollups if possible. First queries the rollup table to retrieve counts. If no valid rollups exist, calls Analytics.getExperimentCounts(com.intuit.wasabi.experimentobjects.Experiment.ID, com.intuit.wasabi.analyticsobjects.Parameters) to do full queries for counts data.
